,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"吓？我地喺條街度係撐義士同前線手足架喎，死7婆不如話一百七十萬人上街係撐警好唔好？c9s"},{"pid":"886bdcb3d3fbc314e07947f867455fa9df1b035d","tid":1486831,"uid":84068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"笑死依家邊有有分 依家係得同路同非同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28c62cdf2fbef64c36aafa1a7a30af29720f027","tid":1486831,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"和理勇武<br />\n予與盾<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"301389f9cf47952819cb6a48ad36ac1fd84345cd","tid":1486831,"uid":21066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dc03bfa0fe38b0a17a2d7597241cbb2418ef37f","tid":1486831,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"我地反應太慢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你試下如果將尋晚互屌ge post轉曬做討論死線/升 級 <br />\n仲會唔會咁<br />\n依家連死線都未定實啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1967910240aa2ee7c827d417938927d41bfb8542","tid":1486831,"uid":306081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d52a3e003662efd3953578ab306539e1fd21fc75","tid":1486831,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"予頭指向政權 唔係黑警<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"84d7b3562d51bab39ae8012e49afe62036f9d322","tid":1486831,"uid":112814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e41365156bc497ee03bda383fc28abdec72df01","tid":1486831,"uid":279938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"吓？我地喺條街度係撐義士同前線手足架喎，死7婆不如話一百七十萬人上街係撐警好唔好？c9s"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"我地點諗點做對家唔care<br />\n事實係對家既文宣機器已經做緊我講既野<br />\n和理遊行對佢地威脅係有 但係最大威脅係和勇並用 而大遊行就俾左正當理由前線升級<br />\n前線既抗爭令黑警中共港共係全世界面前出醜<br />\n爆出一單又一單既醜聞<br />\n中共而家最不滿既就係家醜外傳 仲要搞左兩個月都搞唔撚掂<br />\n而家俾歐美國家拎左黎做新一輪既政治籌碼<br />\n係香港人史無前例既大團結之下<br />\n中共係無法使用致命鎮壓既情況之下<br />\n只有不斷玩分化抹黑恐嚇<br />\n企圖將運動由內部瓦解<br />\n依個係中國獨裁政權玩左幾千年既技術黎<br />\n818係成功 但係成場運動我地都仲係未贏過<br />\n唔好過分樂觀 更唔好有「冇左前線更加好」依個危險念頭<br />\n不分和勇 團結一心<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"eb2d2f4f0aff4567837ece37fce0f88edc95eb67","tid":1486831,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"bb72b9bd7f032a2846e1ba8503cdc7ccb7470567","tid":1486831,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc03bfa0fe38b0a17a2d7597241cbb2418ef37f","tid":1486831,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"我地反應太慢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你試下如果將尋晚互屌ge post轉曬做討論死線/升 級 <br />\n仲會唔會咁<br />\n依家連死線都未定實啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"遲好過冇<br />\n冇大台就會依種缺點'<br />\n但係唔緊要 依家開始都可以接受"},{"pid":"9fddce691b6c131d59b5d996868a2c78acf31999","tid":1486831,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d52a3e003662efd3953578ab306539e1fd21fc75","tid":1486831,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"予頭指向政權 唔係黑警<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"岩 黑警係暴力 但係政權先係始作俑者"},{"pid":"4fe3827dd61b8c5cc189168879eb9f6586026080","tid":1486831,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"818係成功 但係成場運動我地都